## Post 2

**Date:** December 2025 *(based on the LinkedIn activity timestamp)*

**Original Link:**  
https://www.linkedin.com/posts/kevinindig_publishing-data-only-your-product-can-produce-activity-7477372003444789248-D5Ev

### Summary

Kevin emphasizes the value of publishing proprietary data that only a company's product, platform, or customer base can generate. He explains that unique datasets create highly differentiated content, attract backlinks naturally, and establish topical authority because competitors cannot easily replicate the information. The post highlights original research as a sustainable strategy for improving organic visibility in both traditional search and AI-generated search results.

### Main SEO Takeaway

- Publish original data and research to create unique, high-value content.
- Proprietary insights help earn backlinks and strengthen topical authority.
- Exclusive content is more difficult for competitors to replicate.
- Data-driven content performs well for both organic search rankings and AI search visibility.